<template>
  <provide-inject-child />
</template>

<script>
import Provide_Inject_Child from "./Provide_Inject_Child.vue";
export default {
  components: { Provide_Inject_Child },
  data() {
    return {
      items: ["A", "B"],
    };
  },
  provide() {
    return {
      itemLength: this.items.length,
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
